short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get Live Leaderboards for selected Good Good YouTube videos

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Ever wanted to know the live standings in a Good Good Major, depending on the segment of the video you are currently on? 

Well now you can! Using this extension, you will automatically be prompted with a "Good Good" button in the youtube player controls which will render the current standings in the bottom left of the video. 

Currently supported for only the Good Good Cup Major.
